title: First meeting of the Guernsey R Users Group
text: In this first meeting, we will be covering the aims of the Guernsey R Users Group. And, as this probably won’t take the full time, we’ll round off with a quick overview of some of R’s object systems, focusing on S3, S4 and the in-development R7.

title: Guernsey R Users Group
text: This is the website of the Guernsey R Users Group. We’ll post talk materials and details of events here as they are organised.
